@tysonnorris looks like you can use the image `FROM openjdk:8-jdk-alpine`

@csantanapr the adoptopenjdk image you pointed to was `openjdk8-openj9` - I assume that is a j9 one? 

I didn't want to use the version-less tags like `openjdk:8-jdk-alpine`, and did not find one with a version e.g. `8u152-b16` + alpine, but I'm open to suggestions.

Closest I found with openjdk (not j9) + jdk version + alpine is `adoptopenjdk/openjdk8:jdk8u152-b16-alpine`.
